body_html:
From the original message, it seems as though
#include
does not work (without additional work) on Sierra. Is that really true?

Alas, it does work on the High Sierra system with Xcode 9 that I currently have access to,
so it's hard for me to check whether a fix will work.

body:
From the original message, it seems as though 
    #include <mutex>
does not work (without additional work) on Sierra.   Is that really true?

Alas, it does work on the High Sierra system with Xcode 9 that I currently have access to,
so it's hard for me to check whether a fix will work.
